Subject: [ghostium] WebGL readPixels hook

Spec-D wiring. Anchors at top of
``webgl_rendering_context_base.cc``. The real call into
``FingerprintNoiseSource::ApplyWebGLReadPixelsNoise`` lands inside
``ReadPixels`` after the GPU readback completes and before the
resulting bytes are copied into the JS-visible TypedArray.

Format-aware noise: RGBA8 + GL_UNSIGNED_BYTE gets the same ±1 LSB
treatment as Canvas2D; GL_FLOAT gets a 1-ULP mantissa-bit toggle. All
other format/type combinations pass through unchanged (see plan.md
section 4.6).

---
 third_party/blink/renderer/modules/webgl/webgl_rendering_context_base.cc | 6 ++++++
 1 file changed, 6 insertions(+)

